{"type": "article", "id": 19063, "title": "棒球帽躺椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-15T09:27:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110608mFiap7wvor5MCbL1.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是由纽约街头品牌 3sixteen 和家具品牌 Herman Miller 联手推出的躺椅，设计源自用久了棒球手套，有深浅两种颜色和自然的褶皱，里面的天然植物鞣皮会随着时间变暗，外面一层是木板，涂上了古铜色的木油，与浅色皮革正好是两个方向的纹路，很有年代感。目前只制作了三张限量发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145730BP4lvmnwtdeQgcoD.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145731skwJnv4dEzaVjiSW.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145731TUnMaIYqvlmeo9NX.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614573273CBZVcvAyilWHY4.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}